## 2. evidence type HAL — hardware abstraction layer

rationale platform independence at hardware tier. natt os abstracts
host substrate through cell based runtime entry decoupling kernel
from underlying hardware.

observed
- nattos.sira kernel entry: 15866 B
- src/cells/kernel/ files: 315
- src/core/ files: 68
- observation-cell references: 56 files
- audit-cell references: 254 files

interpretation
- nattos sira is inbound kernel entry listens 127.0.0.1:3002 regardless
  of host OS verified ss20260418 commit 2c4fa81
- src cells kernel contains kernel tier abstractions
- observation cell + audit cell sit at boundary isolating substrate
  from upper layers

